Edit a Data Graph

Add related objects and fields to an existing data graph. Save it as a draft and make more changes before building the updated data graph. You can also include data graph metadata in a data kit and copy it to another org instead of manually recreating the metadata. And now you can access data from a data graph through an invocable action in a flow.

Where: This change applies to Data Cloud in Developer, Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited editions.

When: These features become available in July 2024.
